Yes.

761
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:46,240
Your noodles!

762
00:30:48,320 --> 00:30:49,450
With extra noodles.

763
00:30:49,520 --> 00:30:49,840
OK.

764
00:30:49,840 --> 00:30:51,160
Tell me if you want more.

