769
00:30:56,480 --> 00:30:57,960
Haichao's sliced boiled pork with garlic sauce

770
00:30:57,960 --> 00:30:58,840
is great.

771
00:30:58,840 --> 00:30:59,240
Yes!

772
00:30:59,240 --> 00:30:59,970
