00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:06,260
It's great.

776
00:31:06,760 --> 00:31:08,220
Please enjoy it together.

777
00:31:09,600 --> 00:31:10,200
Jianjian,

778
00:31:10,560 --> 00:31:11,440
